{"tid":2199562,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★旺角人頭湧湧 市民讚政府防疫有效！不擔心！","createTime":"2020-09-12T09:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T08:02:16.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"2090ab64622bd70ad48a408e0f3d57fa4672cc43","tid":2199562,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:55:46.000Z","msg":"市民讚政府防疫有效 望公眾積極參與全民檢測<br />\n<br />\n疫情漸趨緩和，陳太今日也攜同二女外出放風。她對限聚令放寬感到高興，指「小朋友留咗好多個月喺屋企」，認為「大家都開心啲，唔洗有咁多規矩」。被問及會否擔心疫情會因放寬限聚令而反覆，陳太直言不擔心，認為應「隨遇而安」。<br />\n<br />\n陳太又稱欣賞政府第三波疫情的防控措施，指措施有效控制疫情擴散。她亦認為公眾應積極參與全民檢測，「唔係睇下自己有冇中嘅問題，而係比政府跟蹤番啲個案，睇下有咩群組」，故她早在計劃開始第一日便前往檢測<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/522821/%E9%99%90%E8%81%9A%E4%BB%A4-%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC%E8%87%B3%E5%9B%9B%E4%BA%BA%E9%A6%96%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E4%BA%BA%E9%A0%AD%E6%B9%A7%E6%B9%A7-%E6%9C%89%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%9B%E6%97%A9%E6%97%A5%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F522821%2F%25E9%2599%2590%25E8%2581%259A%25E4%25BB%25A4-%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25AF%25AC%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%259B%259B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%259C%25AB-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%25B9%25A7%25E6%25B9%25A7-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%259C%259B%25E6%2597%25A9%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9fyrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=80f587d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/522821/%E9%99%90%E8%81%9A%E4%BB%A4-%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC%E8%87%B3%E5%9B%9B%E4%BA%BA%E9%A6%96%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E4%BA%BA%E9%A0%AD%E6%B9%A7%E6%B9%A7-%E6%9C%89%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%9B%E6%97%A9%E6%97%A5%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88</a>"},{"pid":"8652e3a2d71347b3c14c31947bf3c6297f568781","tid":2199562,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTim